name: ITS CORN
description:
It's sibling fighting time, you and your sibling are both corn lover, now spin your corn, eat it all, then grab the next one. You gotta eat more than they do. Good luck.

Player Left:  A/D to move corn left to right, RightShift to grab the next corn.

Player Right:  J/L to move corn left to right, LeftShift to grab the next corn.

Try to stop the other one to get your corn on the plate XD.
